ZH: 在这个城市中，极少数人能够负担起如此豪华的生活。
EN: In this city, only a very small minority can afford such a luxurious lifestyle.

ZH: 这家餐厅的服务质量非常高，所以遭到批评的人是极少数。
EN: The quality of service at this restaurant is very high, so only a very small minority criticize it.

ZH: 在这个领域里，极少数专家有能力解决这个复杂的问题。
EN: In this field, only a very small minority of experts have the ability to solve this complex issue.

ZH: 这个组织的成员基本上都是有社会责任感的人，只有极少数人会违反道德规范。
EN: The members of this organization are mostly socially responsible individuals, with only a very small minority violating ethical standards.

ZH: 这个国家的政策对大多数人都是有利的，但有极少数人受到了不公正的待遇。
EN: The policies of this country are beneficial to the majority, but a very small minority have been treated unfairly.

ZH: 在这个群体中，只有极少数人有权利做出决定。
EN: In this group, only a very small minority have the authority to make decisions.

ZH: 这种情况是非常罕见的，只有极少数人经历过。
EN: This situation is very rare, experienced by only a very small minority.

ZH: 在全球范围内，这种疾病只影响到了极少数人。
EN: Globally, this disease only affects a very small minority of people.

ZH: 在这个公司中，极少数员工有机会得到晋升。
EN: In this company, only a very small minority of employees have the opportunity for promotion.

ZH: 这种观点仅限于极少数人的意见，大多数人都不同意。
EN: This view is limited to the opinions of only a very small minority, with the majority disagreeing.

ZH: 在这个社区中，只有极少数人参加了义工活动。
EN: In this community, only a very small minority participate in volunteer activities.

