EN: There are serious issues with the public transportation system in this city, but only a very small minority are affected.

ZH: 这个科学理论受到广泛认可，只有极少数人提出了异议。
EN: This scientific theory is widely accepted, with only a very small minority raising objections.

ZH: 在这个聚会上，只有极少数人穿着形式服装。
EN: At this party, only a very small minority are dressed in formal attire.

ZH: 在这所学校中，极少数学生拥有这么高的成绩。
EN: In this school, only a very small minority of students have such high grades.

ZH: 这个国家的法律对每个人都适用，不能仅限于极少数人。
EN: The laws of this country apply to everyone, not just a very small minority.

ZH: 这个群体中只有极少数人能够理解这种复杂的概念。
EN: In this group, only a very small minority can understand this complex concept.

ZH: 这个项目的成功要归功于团队的协作，而非极少数人的贡献。
EN: The success of this project is attributed to the team's collaboration, not the contribution of a very small minority.

ZH: 这个城市的空气质量很差，但只有极少数人选择妥善处理废气问题。
EN: The air quality in this city is poor, yet only a very small minority choose to address the issue of emissions properly.

ZH: 在这个研究领域中，只有极少数学者对这个问题有深入的理解。
